data.description: Gorgeous 10 acres of lush green landscape with wild flowers and mature trees are ready to be developed into your dream home and land.  Utilities are already on site, an older septic tank and well are established on the lot.  Note that an oil tank and pony are on the property and mineral rights do NOT belong to the current owner. Placed strategically at the front of the property to not impede on your plans for your land!  Mobile Homes, farm animals, horses all ok on this property.  Go see it today!
